#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:44
msgid "Installation of Cross Binutils"
msgstr "Cross Binutils 설치"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:46
msgid ""
"Go back and re-read the notes in the section titled <xref linkend=\"ch-tools-"
"generalinstructions\"/>.  Understanding the notes labeled important can save "
"you a lot of problems later."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"ch-tools-generalinstructions\"/> 섹션에 있는 노트들을 다시 돌"
"아가서 읽어보십시오. 중요(important) 표시된 노트들을 이해하면 나중에 발생할 "
"수 있는 많은 문제를 막을 수 있습니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:51
msgid ""
"It is important that Binutils be the first package compiled because both "
"Glibc and GCC perform various tests on the available linker and assembler to "
"determine which of their own features to enable."
msgstr ""
"Binutils를 가장 먼저 컴파일하는 것이 중요한데 왜냐면 Glibc와 GCC 모두 사용 가"
"능한 링커와 어셈블러에 대해 다양한 테스트를 수행하여 각각 어떤 기능을 활성화"
"할지 결정하기 때문입니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:56 en/chapter08/binutils.xml:48
msgid ""
"The Binutils documentation recommends building Binutils in a dedicated build "
"directory:"
msgstr ""
"Binutils 문서는 전용 빌드 디렉터리에서 Binutils를 빌드할 것을 권장합니다:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:59 en/chapter05/gcc-pass1.xml:95
#: en/chapter05/glibc.xml:78 en/chapter05/libstdc++.xml:58
#: en/chapter06/binutils-pass2.xml:62 en/chapter06/gcc-pass2.xml:74
#: en/chapter08/binutils.xml:51 en/chapter08/dejagnu.xml:48
#: en/chapter08/e2fsprogs.xml:50 en/chapter08/gcc.xml:60
#: en/chapter08/glibc.xml:68
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">mkdir -v build\n"
"cd       build</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">mkdir -v build\n"
"cd       build</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:63
msgid ""
"In order for the SBU values listed in the rest of the book to be of any use, "
"measure the time it takes to build this package from the configuration, up "
"to and including the first install. To achieve this easily, wrap the "
"commands in a <command>time</command> command like this: <userinput>time "
"{ ../configure ... &amp;&amp; make &amp;&amp; make install; }</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"이후의 책 내용에 나열된 SBU 값이 유용하게 쓰일 수 있도록, 설정(configuration)"
"부터 첫 번째 설치를 포함한 단계까지 이 패키지를 빌드하는 데 걸리는 시간을 측"
"정하십시오. 이를 쉽게 수행하려면, 다음과 같이 명령들을 <command>time</"
"command> 명령으로 감싸십시오: <userinput>time { ../configure ... &amp;&amp; "
"make &amp;&amp; make install; }</userinput>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:71
msgid "Now prepare Binutils for compilation:"
msgstr "이제 Binutils의 컴파일을 준비합니다:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:73
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">../configure --prefix=$LFS/tools \\\n"
"             --with-sysroot=$LFS \\\n"
"             --target=$LFS_TGT   \\\n"
"             --disable-nls       \\\n"
"             --enable-gprofng=no \\\n"
"             --disable-werror    \\\n"
"             --enable-new-dtags  \\\n"
"             --enable-default-hash-style=gnu</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">../configure --prefix=$LFS/tools \\\n"
"             --with-sysroot=$LFS \\\n"
"             --target=$LFS_TGT   \\\n"
"             --disable-nls       \\\n"
"             --enable-gprofng=no \\\n"
"             --disable-werror    \\\n"
"             --enable-new-dtags  \\\n"
"             --enable-default-hash-style=gnu</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><title>
#: en/chapter05/binutils-pass1.xml:83 en/chapter05/gcc-pass1.xml:121
#: en/chapter05/glibc.xml:98 en/chapter05/libstdc++.xml:73
