msgstr "&bzip2-fin-du;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:44
msgid "Installation of Bzip2"
msgstr "Bzip2 설치"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:46
msgid "Apply a patch that will install the documentation for this package:"
msgstr "이 패키지의 문서를 설치하는 패치를 적용:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"pre\">patch -Np1 -i ../&bzip2-docs-patch;</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"pre\">patch -Np1 -i ../&bzip2-docs-patch;</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:50
msgid ""
"The following command ensures installation of symbolic links are relative:"
msgstr "다음 명령어는 심볼릭 링크가 상대 경로로 설치되도록 보장:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i 's@\\(ln -s -f \\)$(PREFIX)/bin/@\\1@' Makefile</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i 's@\\(ln -s -f \\)$(PREFIX)/bin/@\\1@' Makefile</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:54
msgid "Ensure the man pages are installed into the correct location:"
msgstr "man 페이지가 올바른 위치에 설치되도록 보장:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i \"s@(PREFIX)/man@(PREFIX)/share/man@g\" Makefile</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i \"s@(PREFIX)/man@(PREFIX)/share/man@g\" Makefile</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:58
msgid "Prepare Bzip2 for compilation with:"
msgstr "다음 명령어를 사용하여 Bzip2 컴파일을 준비:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"make\">make -f Makefile-libbz2_so\n"
"make clean</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"make\">make -f Makefile-libbz2_so\n"
"make clean</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:67
msgid "<parameter>-f Makefile-libbz2_so</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-f Makefile-libbz2_so</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:69
msgid ""
"This will cause Bzip2 to be built using a different <filename>Makefile</"
"filename> file, in this case the <filename>Makefile-libbz2_so</filename> "
"file, which creates a dynamic <filename class=\"libraryfile\">libbz2.so</"
"filename> library and links the Bzip2 utilities against it."
msgstr ""
"이 작업을 통해 Bzip2 는 다른 <filename>Makefile</filename> 파일(이 경우 "
"<filename>Makefile-libbz2_so</filename> 파일)을 사용하여 빌드됩니다. 이 과정"
"에서 동적 <filename class=\"libraryfile\">libbz2.so</filename> 라이브러리가 "
"생성되며, Bzip2 유틸리티들이 이 라이브러리에 링크됩니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:79
msgid "Compile and test the package:"
msgstr "패키지 컴파일 및 테스트:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:83
msgid "Install the programs:"
msgstr "프로그램 설치:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"install\">make PREFIX=/usr install</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"install\">make PREFIX=/usr install</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:87
msgid "Install the shared library:"
msgstr "공유 라이브러리 설치:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:89
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">cp -av libbz2.so.* /usr/lib\n"
"ln -sv libbz2.so.&bzip2-version; /usr/lib/libbz2.so</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">cp -av libbz2.so.* /usr/lib\n"
"ln -sv libbz2.so.&bzip2-version; /usr/lib/libbz2.so</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:92
msgid ""
"The name of the shared library isn't standardized and it varies among "
"distros.  The instruction above has installed <filename "
"class='libraryfile'>libbz2.so.1.0</filename>, but some applications, for "
"example Kbd, expects a different name <filename "
"class='libraryfile'>libbz2.so.1</filename> that some other distros are "
"using.  Create a compatibility symlink for them:"
msgstr ""
"공유 라이브러리 이름은 표준화되어 있지 않으며 배포판마다 다릅니다. 위의 지침"
"에 따라 <filename class='libraryfile'>libbz2.so.1.0</filename>이 설치되었지"
"만, Kbd 같은 일부 애플리케이션은 다른 배포판에서 사용하는 이름인 <filename "
"class='libraryfile'>libbz2.so.1</filename>을 기대합니다. 이러한 애플리케이션"
"을 위해 호환성 심볼릭 링크를 생성:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:99
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>ln -sv libbz2.so.&bzip2-version; /usr/lib/libbz2.so.1</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>ln -sv libbz2.so.&bzip2-version; /usr/lib/libbz2.so.1</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:102
msgid ""
"The symlink approach is only valid here because the library name difference "
"is a result of different aesthetic views of the distro maintainers, not real "
"ABI incompatibilities.  In general a library name difference most likely "
"indicates an ABI incompatibility and it would be very likely invalid to "
"<quote>hide</quote> the difference via a symlink.  Read <xref "
"linkend='pkgmgmt-upgrade-issues'/> for details about library names."
msgstr ""
"여기서 심볼릭 링크를 사용하는 방식이 유효한 이유는 라이브러리 이름의 차이가 "
"배포판 유지 관리자들의 서로 다른 미적 관점 때문이지, 실제 ABI 호환성 문제 때"
"문이 아니기 때문입니다. 일반적으로 라이브러리 이름의 차이는 ABI 불호환성을 나"
"타낼 가능성이 매우 높으므로, 심볼릭 링크를 통해 그 차이를 <quote>숨기는</"
"quote> 것은 유효하지 않을 가능성이 큽니다. 라이브러리 이름에 대한 자세한 내용"
"은 <xref linkend='pkgmgmt-upgrade-issues'/> 참조."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:112
msgid ""
"Install the shared <command>bzip2</command> binary into the <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/bin</filename> directory, and replace two copies of "
"<command>bzip2</command> with symlinks:"
msgstr ""
"공유 <command>bzip2</command> 바이너리를 <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/"
"bin</filename> 디렉터리에 설치하고, <command>bzip2</command>의 두 복사본을 심"
"볼릭 링크로 교체:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:116
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">cp -v bzip2-shared /usr/bin/bzip2\n"
"for i in /usr/bin/{bzcat,bunzip2}; do\n"
"  ln -sfv bzip2 $i\n"
"done</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">cp -v bzip2-shared /usr/bin/bzip2\n"
"for i in /usr/bin/{bzcat,bunzip2}; do\n"
"  ln -sfv bzip2 $i\n"
"done</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:121 en/chapter08/zlib.xml:60
msgid "Remove a useless static library:"
msgstr "불필요한 정적 라이브러리 제거:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/bzip2.xml:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"install\">rm -fv /usr/lib/libbz2.a</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"install\">rm -fv /usr/lib/libbz2.a</userinput>"

