msgstr "&gmp-fin-du;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:42
msgid "Installation of GMP"
msgstr "GMP 설치"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput><parameter>ABI=32</parameter> ./configure ...</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput><parameter>ABI=32</parameter> ./configure ...</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:45
msgid ""
"If you are building for 32-bit x86, but you have a CPU which is capable of "
"running 64-bit code <emphasis>and</emphasis> you have specified "
"<envar>CFLAGS</envar> in the environment, the configure script will attempt "
"to configure for 64-bits and fail.  Avoid this by invoking the configure "
"command below with <placeholder type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/>"
msgstr ""
"만약 32비트 x86용으로 빌드하고 있지만 64비트 코드를 실행할 수 있는 CPU를 사"
"용 중이고, <emphasis>그리고</emphasis> 환경 변수에 <envar>CFLAGS</envar>를 지"
"정했다면, configure 스크립트는 64비트용으로 설정을 시도하다가 실패할 것입니"
"다. 이를 막으려면 아래의 configure 명령을 <placeholder type=\"screen\" "
"id=\"0\"/> 과 함께 호출하십시오."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:54
msgid ""
"The default settings of GMP produce libraries optimized for the host "
"processor.  If libraries suitable for processors less capable than the "
"host's CPU are desired, generic libraries can be created by appending the "
"<option>--host=none-linux-gnu</option> option to the <command>configure</"
"command> command."
msgstr ""
"GMP의 기본 설정은 호스트 프로세서에 최적화된 라이브러리를 생성합니다. 만약 호"
"스트의 CPU보다 성능이 낮은 프로세서들에 적합한 라이브러리가 필요하다면, "
"<command>configure</command> 명령에 <option>--host=none-linux-gnu</option> 옵"
"션을 추가하여 범용(generic) 라이브러리를 구축할 수 있습니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:65
msgid "First, make an adjustment for compatibility with gcc-15 and later:"
msgstr "먼저, gcc-15 및 그 이후 버전과의 호환성을 위해 설정을 조정:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i '/long long t1;/,+1s/()/(...)/' configure</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i '/long long t1;/,+1s/()/(...)/' configure</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:69
msgid "Prepare GMP for compilation:"
msgstr "GMP 컴파일 준비하기:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:71
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">./configure --prefix=/usr    \\\n"
"            --enable-cxx     \\\n"
"            --disable-static \\\n"
"            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/gmp-&gmp-version;</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">./configure --prefix=/usr    \\\n"
"            --enable-cxx     \\\n"
"            --disable-static \\\n"
"            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/gmp-&gmp-version;</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:80
msgid "<parameter>--enable-cxx</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>--enable-cxx</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:82
msgid "This parameter enables C++ support"
msgstr "이 매개변수는 C++ 지원을 가능하게 함"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:87
msgid "<parameter>--docdir=/usr/share/doc/gmp-&gmp-version;</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>--docdir=/usr/share/doc/gmp-&gmp-version;</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:89
msgid "This variable specifies the correct place for the documentation."
msgstr "이 변수는 문서(documentation)가 저장될 올바른 위치를 지정합니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:96 en/chapter08/mpc.xml:51 en/chapter08/mpfr.xml:51
#: en/chapter08/sed.xml:47
msgid "Compile the package and generate the HTML documentation:"
msgstr "패키지를 컴파일하고 HTML 문서를 생성:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:98 en/chapter08/mpc.xml:53 en/chapter08/mpfr.xml:53
#: en/chapter08/sed.xml:49
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"make\">make\n"
"make html</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"make\">make\n"
"make html</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><important><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:102
msgid ""
"The test suite for GMP in this section is considered critical.  Do not skip "
"it under any circumstances."
msgstr ""
"이 섹션에 있는 GMP 테스트 스위트는 매우 중요한(critical) 것으로 간주됩니다. "
"어떤 상황에서도 이 단계를 건너뛰지 마시오."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"test\">make check 2>&amp;1 | tee gmp-check-log</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"test\">make check 2>&amp;1 | tee gmp-check-log</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><caution><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:110
msgid ""
"The code in gmp is highly optimized for the processor where it is built. "
"Occasionally, the code that detects the processor misidentifies the system "
"capabilities and there will be errors in the tests or other applications "
"using the gmp libraries with the message <computeroutput>Illegal "
"instruction</computeroutput>.  In this case, gmp should be reconfigured with "
"the option <option>--host=none-linux-gnu</option> and rebuilt."
msgstr ""
"GMP 코드는 빌드되는 프로세서에 고도로 최적화되어 있습니다. 때때로 프로세서를 "
"감지하는 코드가 시스템 성능을 잘못 식별하여, 테스트나 GMP 라이브러리를 사용하"
"는 다른 애플리케이션에서 <computeroutput>Illegal instruction</"
"computeroutput> 메시지와 함께 오류가 발생할 수 있습니다. 이 경우, GMP를 "
"<option>--host=none-linux-gnu</option> 옵션과 함께 다시 설정(reconfigure)하"
"고 다시 빌드해야 합니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:120
msgid ""
"Ensure that at least 199 tests in the test suite passed.  Check the results "
"by issuing the following command:"
msgstr ""
"테스트 스위트에서 최소 199개의 테스트가 통과되었는지 확인하십시오. 다음 명령"
"을 실행하여 결과를 확인:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"test\">awk '/# PASS:/{total+=$3} ; END{print total}' gmp-check-log</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"test\">awk '/# PASS:/{total+=$3} ; END{print total}' gmp-check-log</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:125 en/chapter08/mpc.xml:60 en/chapter08/mpfr.xml:65
#: en/chapter08/sed.xml:57
msgid "Install the package and its documentation:"
msgstr "패키지 및 문서 설치:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/gmp.xml:127 en/chapter08/mpc.xml:62 en/chapter08/mpfr.xml:67
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">make install\n"
"make install-html</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">make install\n"
"make install-html</userinput>"

