#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:118
msgid ""
"This package has a test suite, but it can only be run after the package has "
"been installed.  The tests reside in the <filename class=\"directory\">test/"
"</filename> directory.  See the <filename>README</filename> file in that "
"directory for further details."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:129
msgid ""
"The installation of this package will overwrite <filename "
"class=\"libraryfile\">libncursesw.so.&ncurses-base-version;</filename> in-"
"place.  It may crash the shell process which is using code and data from the "
"library file.  Install the package with <literal>DESTDIR</literal>, and "
"replace the library file correctly using the <parameter>--remove-"
"destination</parameter> option of <command>cp</command> (the header "
"<filename>curses.h</filename> is also edited to ensure the wide-character "
"ABI to be used as what we've done in <xref linkend='ch-tools-ncurses'/>):"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:140
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">make DESTDIR=$PWD/dest install\n"
"sed -e 's/^#if.*XOPEN.*$/#if 1/' \\\n"
"    -i dest/usr/include/curses.h\n"
"cp --remove-destination -av dest/* /</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">make DESTDIR=$PWD/dest install\n"
"sed -e 's/^#if.*XOPEN.*$/#if 1/' \\\n"
"    -i dest/usr/include/curses.h\n"
"cp --remove-destination -av dest/* /</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:145
msgid ""
"Many applications still expect the linker to be able to find non-wide-"
"character Ncurses libraries. Trick such applications into linking with wide-"
"character libraries by means of symlinks (note that the <filename "
"class='extension'>.so</filename> links are only safe with "
"<filename>curses.h</filename> edited to always use the wide-character ABI):"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:152
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">for lib in ncurses form panel menu ; do\n"
"    ln -sfv lib${lib}w.so /usr/lib/lib${lib}.so\n"
"    ln -sfv ${lib}w.pc    /usr/lib/pkgconfig/${lib}.pc\n"
"done</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">for lib in ncurses form panel menu ; do\n"
"    ln -sfv lib${lib}w.so /usr/lib/lib${lib}.so\n"
"    ln -sfv ${lib}w.pc    /usr/lib/pkgconfig/${lib}.pc\n"
"done</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:157
msgid ""
"Finally, make sure that old applications that look for <filename "
"class=\"libraryfile\">-lcurses</filename> at build time are still buildable:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:161
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"install\">ln -sfv libncursesw.so /usr/lib/libcurses.so</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"install\">ln -sfv libncursesw.so /usr/lib/libcurses.so</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:163
msgid "If desired, install the Ncurses documentation:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:165
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"install\">cp -v -R doc -T /usr/share/doc/ncurses-&ncurses-version;</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"install\">cp -v -R doc -T /usr/share/doc/ncurses-&ncurses-version;</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:169
msgid ""
"The instructions above don't create non-wide-character Ncurses libraries "
"since no package installed by compiling from sources would link against them "
"at runtime. However, the only known binary-only applications that link "
"against non-wide-character Ncurses libraries require version 5.  If you must "
"have such libraries because of some binary-only application or to be "
"compliant with LSB, build the package again with the following commands:"
msgstr ""
"소스 컴파일을 통해 설치되는 패키지 중 런타임에 이와 링크될 패키지가 없기 때문"
"에, 위의 지침은 와이드 문자를 지원하지 않는(non-wide-character) Ncurses 라이"
"브러리를 생성하지 않습니다. 그러나 와이드 문자를 지원하지 않는 Ncurses 라이브"
"러리와 링크되는 유일하게 알려진 바이너리 전용 애플리케이션은 버전 5를 요구합"
"니다. 만약 바이너리 전용 애플리케이션 때문이거나 LSB 표준을 준수하기 위해 이"
"러한 라이브러리가 반드시 필요하다면, 다음 명령을 사용하여 패키지를 다시 빌드:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><screen>
#: en/chapter08/ncurses.xml:177
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>make distclean\n"
"./configure --prefix=/usr    \\\n"
"            --with-shared    \\\n"
"            --without-normal \\\n"
"            --without-debug  \\\n"
"            --without-cxx-binding \\\n"
"            --with-abi-version=5\n"
"make sources libs\n"
"cp -av lib/lib*.so.5* /usr/lib</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>make distclean\n"
"./configure --prefix=/usr    \\\n"
"            --with-shared    \\\n"
"            --without-normal \\\n"
"            --without-debug  \\\n"
"            --without-cxx-binding \\\n"
"            --with-abi-version=5\n"
"make sources libs\n"
"cp -av lib/lib*.so.5* /usr/lib</userinput>"

