#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:26
msgid ""
"The Patch package contains a program for modifying or creating files by "
"applying a <quote>patch</quote> file typically created by the <command>diff</"
"command> program."
msgstr ""
"Patch 패키지에는 보통 <command>diff</command> 프로그램으로 생성된 "
"<quote>patch</quote> 파일을 적용하여, 파일을 수정하거나 생성하는 프로그램이 "
"들어 있습니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><segmentedlist><seglistitem><seg>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:35
msgid "&patch-fin-sbu;"
msgstr "&patch-fin-sbu;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><segmentedlist><seglistitem><seg>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:36
msgid "&patch-fin-du;"
msgstr "&patch-fin-du;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:64
msgid "Contents of Patch"
msgstr "Patch 구성 요소"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><indexterm><primary>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:70 en/chapter08/patch.xml:87
msgid "patch"
msgstr "patch"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:80
msgid "<command>patch</command>"
msgstr "<command>patch</command>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/patch.xml:82
msgid ""
"Modifies files according to a patch file (A patch file is normally a "
"difference listing created with the <command>diff</command> program. By "
"applying these differences to the original files, <command>patch</command> "
"creates the patched versions.)"
msgstr ""
"패치 파일에 따라 파일을 수정합니다. (패치 파일은 대개 <command>diff</"
"command> 프로그램으로 생성된 차이점 목록입니다. 이러한 차이점을 원본 파일에 "
"적용함으로써, <command>patch</command>는 패치된 버전을 생성합니다.)"

