msgid "Readline-&readline-version;"
msgstr "Readline-&readline-version;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:26
msgid ""
"The Readline package is a set of libraries that offer command-line editing "
"and history capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Readline 패키지는 명령줄 편집 및 히스토리 기능을 제공하는 라이브러리 모음입니"
