#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><segmentedlist><seglistitem><seg>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:34
msgid "&readline-fin-sbu;"
msgstr "&readline-fin-sbu;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><segmentedlist><seglistitem><seg>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:35
msgid "&readline-fin-du;"
msgstr "&readline-fin-du;"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:42
msgid "Installation of Readline"
msgstr "Readline 설치"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:44
msgid ""
"Reinstalling Readline will cause the old libraries to be moved to "
"&lt;libraryname&gt;.old. While this is normally not a problem, in some cases "
"it can trigger a linking bug in <command>ldconfig</command>. This can be "
"avoided by issuing the following two seds:"
msgstr ""
"Readline을 재설치하면 기존 라이브러리들이 &lt;libraryname&gt;.old 로 이동합니"
"다. 대개 문제가 되지 않지만, 일부 경우 <command>ldconfig</command>에서 링크 "
"오류(linking bug) 될 수 있습니다. 이를 막으려면 다음 두 가지 sed 명령을 실행:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:49
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i '/MV.*old/d' Makefile.in\n"
"sed -i '/{OLDSUFF}/c:' support/shlib-install</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i '/MV.*old/d' Makefile.in\n"
"sed -i '/{OLDSUFF}/c:' support/shlib-install</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:52
msgid ""
"Prevent hard coding library search paths (rpath) into the shared libraries.  "
"This package does not need rpath for an installation into the standard "
"location, and rpath may sometimes cause unwanted effects or even security "
"issues:"
msgstr ""
"공유 라이브러리에 라이브러리 검색 경로(rpath)를 하드 코딩하는 것을 막습니다. "
"이 패키지는 표준 위치에 설치할 때는 rpath가 필요하지 않으며, rpath는 때때로 "
"원치 않는 부작용이나 보안 문제를 일으킬 수 있습니다:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>sed -i 's/-Wl,-rpath,[^ ]*//' support/shobj-conf</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>sed -i 's/-Wl,-rpath,[^ ]*//' support/shobj-conf</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:60
msgid ""
"Fix a problem identified upstream specifically for this version of readline:"
msgstr "이 버전의 Readline에 대해 업스트림에서 확인된 문제를 수정:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:63
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>sed -e '270a\\\n"
"     else\\\n"
"       chars_avail = 1;'      \\\n"
"    -e '288i\\   result = -1;' \\\n"
"    -i.orig input.c</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>sed -e '270a\\\n"
"     else\\\n"
"       chars_avail = 1;'      \\\n"
"    -e '288i\\   result = -1;' \\\n"
"    -i.orig input.c</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:69
msgid "Prepare Readline for compilation:"
msgstr "Readline 컴파일 준비하기:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:71
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">./configure --prefix=/usr    \\\n"
"            --disable-static \\\n"
"            --with-curses    \\\n"
"            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/readline-&readline-version;</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">./configure --prefix=/usr    \\\n"
"            --disable-static \\\n"
"            --with-curses    \\\n"
"            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/readline-&readline-version;</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:80
msgid "<parameter>--with-curses</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>--with-curses</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:82
msgid ""
"This option tells Readline that it can find the termcap library functions in "
"the curses library, not a separate termcap library. This will generate the "
"correct <filename>readline.pc</filename> file."
msgstr ""
"이 옵션은 Readline이 별도의 termcap 라이브러리가 아니라, curses 라이브러리에"
"서 termcap 라이브러리 함수를 찾을 수 있음을 말합니다. 이것은 올바른 "
"<filename>readline.pc</filename> 파일을 생성합니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:93
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"make\">make SHLIB_LIBS=\"-lncursesw\"</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"make\">make SHLIB_LIBS=\"-lncursesw\"</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:99
msgid "<parameter>SHLIB_LIBS=\"-lncursesw\"</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>SHLIB_LIBS=\"-lncursesw\"</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/readline.xml:101
msgid ""
"This option forces Readline to link against the <filename "
"class=\"libraryfile\">libncursesw</filename> library.  For details see the "
"<quote>Shared Libraries</quote> section in the package's <filename>README</"
"filename> file."
msgstr ""
"이 옵션은 ReadLine이 <filename class=\"libraryfile\">libncursesw</filename> "
"라이브러리와 연결되도록 강제합니다. 자세한 내용은 패키지의 <filename>README</"
"filename> 파일 안에서 <quote>Shared Libraries</quote> 섹션을 참조하십시오."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
