#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:240
msgid "libudev.so"
msgstr "libudev.so"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><segmentedlist><seglistitem><seg>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:242
msgid "/etc/udev and /usr/lib/udev"
msgstr "/etc/udev 및 /usr/lib/udev"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:253
msgid ""
"Generic udev administration tool: controls the udevd daemon, provides info "
"from the Udev database, monitors uevents, waits for uevents to finish, tests "
"Udev configuration, and triggers uevents for a given device"
msgstr ""
"일반 udev 관리 도구: udevd 데몬을 제어하고, Udev 데이터베이스로부터 정보를 제"
"공하며, uevent를 모니터링하고, uevent가 끝날 때까지 기다리며, Udev 설정을 테"
"스트하고, 지정된 장치에 대한 uevent를 발생"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:264
msgid "<command>udevd</command>"
msgstr "<command>udevd</command>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:266
msgid ""
"A daemon that listens for uevents on the netlink socket, creates devices and "
"runs the configured external programs in response to these uevents"
msgstr ""
"넷링크(netlink) 소켓에서 uevent를 리스닝(listening)하고, 장치를 생성하며, 이"
"러한 uevent에 대응하여 설정된 외부 프로그램들을 실행하는 데몬"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><indexterm><primary>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:270
msgid "udevd"
msgstr "udevd"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:276
msgid "<command>udev-hwdb</command>"
msgstr "<command>udev-hwdb</command>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:278
msgid "Updates or queries the hardware database."
msgstr "하드웨어 데이터베이스를 업데이트 또는 쿼리."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><indexterm><primary>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:280
msgid "udev-hwdb"
msgstr "udev-hwdb"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/udev.xml:288
