#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:50
msgid "Installation of Vim"
msgstr "Vim 설치"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:52
msgid ""
"First, change the default location of the <filename>vimrc</filename> "
"configuration file to <filename class=\"directory\">/etc</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"우선, <filename>vimrc</filename> 설정 파일의 기본 위치를 <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/etc</filename>로 변경:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"pre\">echo '#define SYS_VIMRC_FILE \"/etc/vimrc\"' &gt;&gt; src/feature.h</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"pre\">echo '#define SYS_VIMRC_FILE \"/etc/vimrc\"' &gt;&gt; src/feature.h</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:57
msgid "Prepare Vim for compilation:"
msgstr "Vim 컴파일 준비하기:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:65
msgid ""
"To prepare the tests, ensure that user <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">tester</systemitem> can write to the source tree and "
"exclude one file containing tests requiring <command>curl</command> or "
"<command>wget</command>:"
msgstr ""
"테스트를 준비하려면, <systemitem class=\"username\">tester</systemitem> 사용"
"자가 소스 트리에 쓸 수 있는지 확인하고, <command>curl</command> 또는 "
"<command>wget</command>이 필요한 테스트가 들어간 파일 하나를 제외:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:70
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"test\">chown -R tester .\n"
"sed '/test_plugin_glvs/d' -i src/testdir/Make_all.mak</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"test\">chown -R tester .\n"
"sed '/test_plugin_glvs/d' -i src/testdir/Make_all.mak</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:73
msgid ""
"Now run the tests as user <systemitem class=\"username\">tester</systemitem>:"
msgstr ""
"이제 <systemitem class=\"username\">tester</systemitem> 사용자로 테스트를 실"
"행:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:76
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"test\">su tester -c \"TERM=xterm-256color LANG=en_US.UTF-8 make -j1 test\" \\\n"
"   &amp;> vim-test.log</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"test\">su tester -c \"TERM=xterm-256color LANG=en_US.UTF-8 make -j1 test\" \\\n"
"   &amp;> vim-test.log</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:79
msgid ""
"The test suite outputs a lot of binary data to the screen.  This can cause "
"issues with the settings of the current terminal (especially while we are "
"overriding the <envar>TERM</envar> variable to satisfy some assumptions of "
"the test suite).  The problem can be avoided by redirecting the output to a "
"log file as shown above.  A successful test will result in the words "
"<computeroutput>ALL DONE</computeroutput> in the log file at completion."
msgstr ""
"테스트 도구 모음(test suite)은 화면에 많은 이진 데이터를 출력합니다. 이는 현"
"재 터미널의 설정에 문제를 일으킬 수 있습니다(특히 테스트 도구 모음의 일부 가"
"정을 충족하기 위해 <envar>TERM</envar> 변수를 무시하고 설정하는 동안에는 더"
"욱 그렇습니다). 이 문제는 위에서 보여준 것처럼 출력을 로그 파일로 리디렉트하"
"여 피할 수 있습니다. 테스트가 성공하면 완료 시 로그 파일에 "
"<computeroutput>ALL DONE</computeroutput>이라는 문구가 나옵니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:87
msgid "One test, test_matchfuzzy.vim, is known to fail on some systems."
msgstr ""
"한 테스트 test_matchfuzzy.vim 은 일부 시스템에서 실패하는 것으로 알려져 있습"
"니다."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:93
msgid ""
"Many users reflexively type <command>vi</command> instead of <command>vim</"
"command>. To allow execution of <command>vim</command> when users habitually "
"enter <command>vi</command>, create a symlink for both the binary and the "
"man page in the provided languages:"
msgstr ""
"많은 사용자가 반사적으로 <command>vim</command> 대신 <command>vi</command>를 "
"입력하곤 합니다. 사용자가 평소 습관대로 <command>vi</command>를 입력하더라도 "
"<command>vim</command>이 실행될 수 있도록, 바이너리와 제공된 언어별 매뉴얼 페"
"이지(man page) 모두에 대한 심볼릭 링크(symlink)를 생성:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:99
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">ln -sv vim /usr/bin/vi\n"
"for L in  /usr/share/man/{,*/}man1/vim.1; do\n"
"    ln -sv vim.1 $(dirname $L)/vi.1\n"
"done</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">ln -sv vim /usr/bin/vi\n"
"for L in  /usr/share/man/{,*/}man1/vim.1; do\n"
"    ln -sv vim.1 $(dirname $L)/vi.1\n"
"done</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:104
msgid ""
"By default, Vim's documentation is installed in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/share/vim</filename>. The following symlink allows "
"the documentation to be accessed via <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/"
"share/doc/vim-&vim-version;</filename>, making it consistent with the "
"location of documentation for other packages:"
msgstr ""
"By default, Vim's documentation is installed in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/share/vim</filename>. The following symlink allows "
"the documentation to be accessed via <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/"
"share/doc/vim-&vim-version;</filename>, making it consistent with the "
"location of documentation for other packages:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"install\">ln -sv ../&vim-docdir;/doc /usr/share/doc/vim-&vim-version;</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"install\">ln -sv ../&vim-docdir;/doc /usr/share/doc/vim-&vim-version;</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:112
msgid ""
"If an X Window System is going to be installed on the LFS system, it may be "
"necessary to recompile Vim after installing X. Vim comes with a GUI version "
"of the editor that requires X and some additional libraries to be installed. "
"For more information on this process, refer to the Vim documentation and the "
"Vim installation page in the BLFS book at <ulink url=\"&blfs-book;postlfs/"
"vim.html\"/>."
msgstr ""
"LFS 시스템에 X 윈도우 시스템(X Window System)을 설치할 예정이라면, X 설치 후 "
"Vim을 다시 컴파일해야 할 수도 있습니다. Vim은 X와 몇몇 추가 라이브러리의 설치"
"가 필요한 GUI 버전의 편집기를 함께 제공합니다. 이 과정에 대한 더 자세한 내용"
"은 Vim 문서와 <ulink url=\"&blfs-book;postlfs/vim.html\"/> 에 있는 BLFS book"
"의 Vim 설치 페이지를 참고하십시오."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:123
msgid "Configuring Vim"
msgstr "Vim 설정"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:126 en/chapter11/reboot.xml:97
msgid "/etc/vimrc"
msgstr "/etc/vimrc"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:129
msgid ""
"By default, <command>vim</command> runs in vi-incompatible mode.  This may "
"be new to users who have used other editors in the past. The "
"<quote>nocompatible</quote> setting is included below to highlight the fact "
"that a new behavior is being used. It also reminds those who would change to "
"<quote>compatible</quote> mode that it should be the first setting in the "
"configuration file. This is necessary because it changes other settings, and "
"overrides must come after this setting. Create a default <command>vim</"
"command> configuration file by running the following:"
msgstr ""
"By default, <command>vim</command> runs in vi-incompatible mode.  This may "
"be new to users who have used other editors in the past. The "
"<quote>nocompatible</quote> setting is included below to highlight the fact "
"that a new behavior is being used. It also reminds those who would change to "
"<quote>compatible</quote> mode that it should be the first setting in the "
"configuration file. This is necessary because it changes other settings, and "
"overrides must come after this setting. Create a default <command>vim</"
"command> configuration file by running the following:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:138
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput>cat &gt; /etc/vimrc &lt;&lt; \"EOF\"\n"
"<literal>\" Begin /etc/vimrc\n"
"\n"
"\" Ensure defaults are set before customizing settings, not after\n"
"source $VIMRUNTIME/defaults.vim\n"
"let skip_defaults_vim=1\n"
"\n"
"set nocompatible\n"
"set backspace=2\n"
"set mouse=\n"
"syntax on\n"
"if (&amp;term == \"xterm\") || (&amp;term == \"putty\")\n"
"  set background=dark\n"
"endif\n"
"\n"
"\" End /etc/vimrc</literal>\n"
"EOF</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>cat &gt; /etc/vimrc &lt;&lt; \"EOF\"\n"
"<literal>\" Begin /etc/vimrc\n"
"\n"
"\" Ensure defaults are set before customizing settings, not after\n"
"source $VIMRUNTIME/defaults.vim\n"
"let skip_defaults_vim=1\n"
"\n"
"set nocompatible\n"
"set backspace=2\n"
"set mouse=\n"
"syntax on\n"
"if (&amp;term == \"xterm\") || (&amp;term == \"putty\")\n"
"  set background=dark\n"
"endif\n"
"\n"
"\" End /etc/vimrc</literal>\n"
"EOF</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: en/chapter08/vim.xml:156
msgid ""
"The <parameter>set nocompatible</parameter> setting makes <command>vim</"
"command> behave in a more useful way (the default) than the vi-compatible "
"manner. Remove the <quote>no</quote> to keep the old <command>vi</command> "
"behavior. The <parameter>set backspace=2</parameter> setting allows "
"backspacing over line breaks, autoindents, and the start of an insert. The "
"<parameter>syntax on</parameter> parameter enables vim's syntax "
"highlighting.  The <parameter>set mouse=</parameter> setting enables proper "
"pasting of text with the mouse when working in chroot or over a remote "
"connection.  Finally, the <emphasis>if</emphasis> statement with the "
"<parameter>set background=dark</parameter> setting corrects <command>vim</"
"command>'s guess about the background color of some terminal emulators. This "
"gives the highlighting a better color scheme for use on the black background "
"of these programs."
msgstr ""
"<parameter>set nocompatible</parameter> 설정은 <command>vim</command>이 vi 호"
"환 방식보다 더 유용한 방식(기본값)으로 동작하게 합니다. 기존의 <command>vi</"
"command> 동작 방식을 유지하려면 <quote>no</quote>를 제거하십시오. "
"<parameter>set backspace=2</parameter> 설정은 줄 바꿈, 자동 들여쓰기, 삽입 시"
"작 지점에서도 백스페이스를 사용할 수 있게 합니다. <parameter>syntax on</"
"parameter> 매개변수는 vim의 구문 강조(syntax highlighting) 기능을 활성화합니"
"다. <parameter>set mouse=</parameter> 설정은 chroot 환경이나 원격 접속 시 마"
"우스로 텍스트를 제대로 붙여넣을 수 있게 합니다. 마지막으로, <parameter>set "
"background=dark</parameter> 설정을 포함한 <emphasis>if</emphasis> 문은 일부 "
"터미널 에뮬레이터의 배경색에 대한 <command>vim</command>의 추측을 교정합니"
"다. 이를 통해 해당 프로그램의 검은색 배경에서 구문 강조가 더 보기 좋은 색상으"
"로 표시됩니다."

